## chart main Project Status Crux
```mermaid
flowchart LR
  bounty["Bounty: managed Instagram creator outreach"]
  api["GREEN API control plane MVP"]
  delivery["RED Real delivery adapter missing"]
  ops["RED Sender operations missing"]
  beads["YELLOW Beads planning active"]
  next["Next: persistent store + delivery adapter"]
  bounty --> api
  bounty --> delivery
  bounty --> ops
  delivery --> beads
  ops --> beads
  beads --> next
  class api green
  class delivery red
  class ops red
  class beads yellow
  classDef green fill:#dff7df,stroke:#20833a,stroke-width:2px,color:#0f2f18
  classDef yellow fill:#fff3bf,stroke:#b7791f,stroke-width:2px,color:#3a2a00
  classDef red fill:#ffd6d6,stroke:#c53030,stroke-width:2px,color:#3a0505
```

## chart epic-gantt Epic Status
```mermaid
gantt
  title Inschneidergram Epic Status
  dateFormat YYYY-MM-DD
  section GREEN Working
  GREEN Campaign API MVP :done, 2026-05-30, 1d
  section YELLOW Bead-covered gaps
  YELLOW Product docs and task graph :active, 2026-05-30, 2d
  section RED Unproven
  RED Real delivery adapter :crit, 2026-06-01, 5d
  RED Pilot evidence :crit, 2026-06-06, 4d
```

## chart epic-map Epic Dependency Map
